#  Write a program to create a new string made of the middle three characters of an input string of odd length

name = input("Enter the name : ")

n = len(name) # To measure length of input

mid = n // 2

just_left = name[mid - 1] # Just left character from middle character
middle = name[mid] # Middle character
just_right = name[mid + 1] # Just right character from middle character

print(just_left + middle + just_right)
